# Authentication Flow Testing
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = Content-Type: application/json

### 1. Test NextAuth Providers Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/providers

### 2. Test NextAuth Session Endpoint  
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session

### 3. Test NextAuth CSRF Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/csrf

### 4. Test NextAuth Signin Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin

### 5. Test NextAuth Signout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signout
{{contentType}}

{
  "csrfToken": "your-csrf-token-here"
}

### 6. Test Custom Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
{{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123",
  "name": "Test User"
}

### 7. Test Custom Email Verification
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-email?token=your-verification-token

### 8. Test Custom Forgot Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/forgot-password
{{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 9. Test Custom Reset Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/reset-password
{{contentType}}

{
  "token": "your-reset-token",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123"
}

### 10. Test Credentials Login (requires form data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/callback/credentials
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

csrfToken=your-csrf-token&email=test@example.com&password=TestPassword123&callbackUrl={{baseUrl}}&json=true